sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 🧑 User / CLI
    participant Manager as BertIndexManager
    participant Sharded as ShardedIndex
    participant Bert as BertIndex
    participant Disk as 💾 Disk (HNSW + Offsets + Sentences)

    User->>Manager: flush_all()
    Manager->>Sharded: flush_all()
    loop For each shard
        Sharded->>Bert: flush()
        alt dirty_count > 0
            Bert->>Disk: save() (HNSW)
            Bert->>Disk: offsets->flush()

